'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales sun ji tsoron shiga cikin 'yan bindiga
Akwai takaici daga wasu 'yan majalisa na Wales (AM) game da shawarar da aka yi cewa za a canza sunansa zuwa MWP (Majalisa na Wales).
Tushen wannan takaddama na cikin tsare-tsaren sauya sunan majalisa zuwa "Majalisar Wales".
Wasu 'yan majalisa daga kowane bangare na siyasa suna tsoron cewa hakan zai sa su zama abin dariya.
Wani jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya ce kungiyar tana da damuwa game da yadda ake kiran wannan jam'iyyar Twp da Pwp".
Ga masu karatu da ba na Welsh ba: a harshen Welsh, twp na nufin wauta kuma pwp na nufin ƙazanta.
Wani babban jami'in Plaid ya ce kungiyar baki daya "ba ta jin dadin hakan" kuma ya ba da shawarar wasu hanyoyin.
Wani dan majalisa na Conservative na Wales ya ce kungiyar ta kasance mai 'ruhaniya' game da sauya sunan, amma ya ce MWP suna da kusanci da Muppet (Marreta).
A wannan mahallin, harafin w a cikin yaren Welsh yana da irin wannan furcin kamar harafin u a cikin Turanci na Yorkshire.
Kwamitin Majalisar, wanda ke shirin kafa dokokin da za su kawo sauye-sauyen sunayen, ya ce: "Abin da ya kamata a yanke shawara a kan yadda za a nada 'yan majalisar shi ne za a yanke shi".
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba majalisarta ikon sauya sunan.
