A bayan girgizar kasa ta Lombok, alal misali, an gaya wa kungiyoyi masu zaman kansu na kasashen waje cewa ba su da bukata.
Ko da yake an kori sama da kashi 10 cikin 100 na mutanen Lombok, ba a ayyana bala'in kasa ba, abin da ake bukata don samun taimakon ƙasashen waje.
"A wasu lokatai, sun bayyana sarai cewa ba sa neman taimakon kasa da kasa, saboda haka yana da wuya", in ji Ms Sumbung.
Ko da yake kungiyar Save the Children tana shirya tawagar da za ta kai wa Palu hari, babu tabbacin cewa ma'aikatan kasashen waje za su iya yin aiki a kan filin.
Mr. Sutopo, mai magana da yawun hukumar bada agajin bala'i ta kasa ya ce hukumomin Indonesia suna tantance halin da ake ciki a Palu domin ganin ko za a kyale hukumomin kasa da kasa su taimaka wajen aikin agaji.
Duk da girgizar ƙasa da ke ta addabar Indonesia, ƙasar ba ta da shiri sosai don halayen yanayi.
Ko da yake an gina su a Aceh, ba a yawan ganin mafaka a wasu yankunan bakin teku.
Wataƙila rashin fitowar wata siginar gargadin tsunami a Palu, da rashin amincewar da aka yi na yin gargadin, ya taimaka wajen asarar rayuka.
A lokatai masu kyau, yin tafiya tsakanin tsibirai da yawa na ƙasar Indonesiya yana da ƙalubale.
Bala'i na halitta ya sa aiki ya yi wuya.
Jirgin asibiti da ke Lombok don kula da wadanda girgizar kasa ta shafa yana kan hanyarsa zuwa Palu, amma zai dauki akalla kwanaki uku kafin ya isa wurin da wannan sabon bala'i ya faru.
Shugaba Joko Widodo, wanda ya sanya ingantaccen kayan aikin da ya lalace a tsakiyar yakin neman zabensa, ya kashe makudan kudade a kan hanyoyi da hanyoyin jirgin kasa.
Amma rashin kudade ya ci karo da shugaban Joko yayin da yake fuskantar sake zabensa a shekara mai zuwa.
Shugaban na fuskantar matsin lamba saboda tsananin rikice-rikicen addinai a Indonesia, inda 'yan Musulmi da suka fi rinjaye suka karɓi wani addini mai ra'ayin mazan jiya.
Fiye da mutane 1,000 suka mutu kuma dubun dubatan suka rasa gidajensu yayin da ƙungiyoyin Krista da Musulmai suka yi yaƙi a kan tituna ta amfani da katane, baka da kibiyoyi da sauran makamai masu banƙyama.
Duba: Daniel Sturridge na Liverpool ya yi dogon harbi don ci gaban Chelsea
Daniel Sturridge ya ceci Liverpool daga shan kashi a gasar Premier ta Ingila da Chelsea, da kwallo a minti na 89 a ranar Asabar a filin wasa na Stamford Bridge da ke birnin London.
Sturridge ya karbi wani wasa daga Xherdan Shaqiri lokacin da yake kusan mita 30 daga ragar Chelsea, inda tawagarsa ta yi rashin nasara da ci 1-0.
Ya yi taɓawa a gefen hagu kafin ya yi taƙama zuwa ga na biyu.
A ƙoƙarin, ƙwallon ya tashi sama da babban yanki yayin da yake tafiya zuwa kusurwar dama ta sama.
A ƙarshe, ƙwallon ya faɗi a kan Kepa Arrizabalaga a cikin jirgin kuma ya faɗi cikin raga.
"Ina kokarin samun wannan matsayin ne kawai, don zuwa kwallon, kuma 'yan wasa kamar Shaq suna ci gaba sosai, don haka kawai ina samun lokaci mai yawa", in ji Sturridge ga LiverpoolFC.com.
"Na ga Kante yana zuwa, na yi taɓawa, ban yi tunani sosai ba. Na gama kawai".
Chelsea ta ci 1-0 a lokacin da aka tashi daga raga bayan da Eden Hazard ya ci kwallo a minti na 25.
A wannan wasa, dan wasan ya yi wa Mateo Kovacic kwallo a baya kafin ya yi birgima a kusa da tsakiyar filin wasan kuma ya yi tsere zuwa Liverpool.
Kovacic ya yi wani gagarumin wasa a tsakiyar filin wasa.
Sai ya yi wani kyakkyawan harbi wanda ya ratsa kariya ta baya, ya kai Hazard zuwa babban yanki.
Ya tsallake tsaron kuma ya ci kwallo a raga ta biyu tare da bugun ƙafar hagu wanda ya ratsa mai tsaron gidan Alisson Becker na Liverpool.
Liverpool za ta kara da Napoli a zagayen rukuni na gasar zakarun Turai a karfe uku na yammacin Laraba a filin wasa na San Paolo a birnin Naples na Italiya.
Chelsea za ta fafata da Videoton a gasar zakarun Turai a ranar Alhamis da karfe uku na yamma a birnin Landan.
Mutane 832 Sun Mutu A Tsunami A Indonesia
Adadin mutanen da suka mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami a Indonesia ya kai 832, in ji hukumar bada agajin bala'i ta kasar a farkon ranar Lahadi.
Rahotanni sun bayyana cewa mutane da dama sun makale a cikin rugujewar gine-gine da suka rushe a lokacin girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5 da ta afku a ranar Juma'a, wanda ya haifar da raƙuman ruwa masu tsayi mita 6, in ji Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, mai magana da yawun hukumar a wani taron manema labarai.
An rufe birnin Palu, mai mutane fiye da 380,000, da tarun gine-gine da suka rushe.
'Yan sanda sun kama wani mutum mai shekaru 32 da haihuwa bisa zargin kisan kai bayan sun yi wa wata mata bulala har ta mutu
An fara binciken kisan kai bayan da aka gano gawar wata mata a Birkenhead, Merseyside, da safiyar yau.
An gano wanda aka kashe a karfe 7:55 na safe a garin Grayson Mews da ke kan titin John, kuma an kama wani mutum mai shekara 32 da ake zargi da kisan kai.
'Yan sanda sun bukaci duk wani mutum da ya ga wani abu a wurin ya ba da bayanin.
Wani mai bincike mai suna Brian O'Hagan ya ce: "Binciken yana kan farko, amma ina so in kira duk wanda ke cikin unguwar John Street a Birkenhead da ya ga wani abu mai ban mamaki ya tuntube mu.
Ina kuma kira ga duk wanda ya samu hotuna daga kyamarar jirgin sama, musamman masu motocin taksi, su tuntube mu domin suna iya samun bayanai masu muhimmanci ga binciken".
Wani mai magana da yawun 'yan sanda ya tabbatar da cewa matar da aka gano jikinta mazauniyar Birkenhead ce kuma an gano ta a cikin wani gida.
Da yamma, abokai da suke ganin sun san wanda aka kashe sun je wurin don su nemi inda aka same ta da safe.
Ana ci gaba da bincike, kuma 'yan sanda sun ce a yanzu haka suna sanar da dangin wanda aka kashe.
Wani direban taksi da ke zaune a Grayson Mews ya yi kokarin shiga gidansa, amma 'yan sanda sun sanar da shi cewa an hana shi shiga ko fita daga ginin.
Sa'ad da aka gaya masa abin da ya faru, sai ya yi mamaki.
An sanar da mazauna garin cewa za su iya komawa gidajensu cikin sa'o'i kadan.
An ji wani jami'in 'yan sanda yana gaya wa wani mutum cewa an riga an yi wa dukan yankin kallon wurin da aka yi kisan kai.
Wata mata ta zo wurin tana kuka.
Ya ce, "Wannan abin ban tsoro ne".
Da ƙarfe biyu na yamma, motocin 'yan sanda biyu suna cikin layin kuma wani yana tsaye a waje.
An tura wasu jami'an 'yan sanda a cikin shingen don su tsare ginin.
