"Babban abin da ke jawo haɗarin Rosa ko kuma abin da ya rage daga ita shi ne ruwan sama mai yawa a Baja California, Sonora ta arewa maso yamma, da kuma kudu maso yammacin hamada na Amirka", in ji National Hurricane Center.
An annabta cewa wannan ruwan sama zai kawo ambaliyar ruwa mai saurin zubewa da kuma ɓarnar da ke jefa rai cikin haɗari a hamada da kuma halaka a kan tuddai.
