Kanye West: Rapper ya sauya sunansa zuwa Ye
Wani mawaki mai suna Kanye West ya canja sunansa zuwa Ye.
Da yake sanar da wannan canji a shafinsa na Twitter a ranar Asabar, ya rubuta: "Wanda a baya ake kira Kanye West".
West, mai shekara 41, ya sami sunan lakabi na Ye na ɗan lokaci kuma ya yi amfani da shi azaman taken kundin wakarsa na takwas, wanda aka fitar a watan Yuni.
Canjin ya zo ne kafin halartarsa a ranar Asabar da Daren Rayuwa, inda ake hasashen zai gabatar da sabon kundin wakarsa na Yandhi.
Wannan aikin na nufin maye gurbin na mawaƙa Ariana Grande, wanda ya soke shi saboda "dalilan motsin rai", in ji mai shirya wasan kwaikwayon.
Da yake yana da ɗan gajeren sunan sana'arsa na yanzu, kalmar tana da ma'ana ta addini a gare shi, a cewar West.
"Ina tsammanin 'ye' ita ce kalma da aka fi amfani da ita a cikin Littafi Mai Tsarki, kuma a cikin Littafi Mai Tsarki tana nufin 'ka,'" in ji West a farkon wannan shekara, sa'ad da yake magana game da taken littafinsa a gaban mai gabatar da rediyo Big Boy.
"Don haka, ni ne kai, ni ne mu, mu ne mu.
Yana fitowa daga Kanye, wanda ke nufin "wannan", don kawai Ye - kasancewa kawai tunani na nagarta, mugunta, rikicewarmu, komai.
Wannan kundin ya fi nuna ko wane ne mu".
