Ayr 38 - 17 Melrose: Ayr mai nasara ya kai ga saman
Wasannin farko biyu da aka yi a baya sun gurbata sakamakon, amma babu shakka Ayr sun cancanci nasara a wannan wasa mai ban sha'awa na Tennent's Premiership na yau.
Yanzu haka, tawagar tana kan gaba a gasar, ita kaɗai ce a cikin goma da ba ta ci kofin ba.
A ƙarshe, ya kasance mafi kyau tsaro da kuma mafi alhẽri hadarin management cewa sanya gida tawagar yi mafi alhẽri, kuma kocin Peter Murchie yana da dukan dalilin zama gamsu.
"An gwada mu a wasanninmu har zuwa yanzu kuma har yanzu ba za a iya doke mu ba, don haka dole ne in yi farin ciki", in ji shi.
