Grant Anderson a minti na 14 wanda Frazier Climo ya canza ya sanya Ayr a gaba, amma katin rawaya ga kyaftin din Scotland Rory Hughes, wanda Warriors suka yi watsi da shi, ya ba Melrose damar bayyana lambobin, kuma Jason Baggot ya yi amfani da gwajin da ba a canza shi ba.
