Wata mata da aka yi mata allurar rigakafin, wadda take koya wa tsarin garkuwarta gane ƙwayoyin cuta masu cutarwa, ta ga ciwon daji na cikin mahaifarta ya ɓace na fiye da watanni 18.
Wannan hanyar tana ɗaukan ƙwayoyin cuta daga wani mai ciwon daji kuma a canja su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje don su iya ganin furotin da ake kira HER2 da ke da amfani a yawancin cututtukan daji.
Farfesa Jay Berzofsky na Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon daji ta Amirka a Bethesda, Maryland, ya ce: "Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa muna da rigakafin da ke da kyau".
HER2 tana "sarrafa ciwon daji iri-iri", har da na nono, na mahaifa, na huhu, da kuma na ciwon daji na jini, in ji Farfesa Berzofsky.
Irin wannan tsarin da ake amfani da shi wajen cire ƙwayoyin cuta daga marasa lafiya kuma a "koyar da su" su kai wa ƙwayoyin ciwon daji hari ya yi aiki wajen magance wani irin cutar sankarar bargo.
Kanye West ya fara jawabin goyon bayan Trump da hat na MAGA bayan fitowarsa a SNL.
Bai tafi daidai ba.
An yi wa Kanye West barazanar nunawa a gidan rediyon Saturday Night Live bayan wani wasan kwaikwayon da ya yi wanda ya nuna cewa yana yabon shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, inda ya ce zai tsaya takarar shugaban kasa a 2020.
Bayan da ta yi waka a daren, mai suna "Ghost Town", inda ta saka hat da ke cewa "Make America Great", ta fara wani hargitsi da 'yan Democrat kuma ta sake jaddada goyon bayanta ga Trump.
"Na yi magana da fararen fata sau da yawa, sai ya ce, "Ta yaya za ka so Trump?
"Da na damu da wariyar launin fata, da na bar Amirka tun da daɗewa", in ji shi.
SNL ta fara ne da wani fim na satire da Matt Damon, wanda a ciki tauraron Hollywood ya yi ba'a da shaidar Brett Kavanaugh a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i da Christine Blasey Ford ta yi.
Ko da yake ba a watsa shi ba, an buga wasan kwaikwayon wasan kwaikwayon na West a kan kafofin watsa labarun ta hanyar dan wasan kwaikwayo Chris Rock.
Ba a san ko Rock yana so ya yi wa West ba'a ba sa'ad da ya yi hakan.
