Maganganunsa sun jawo hayaniya daga jama'a kuma masu halartar SNL sun bayyana sun kunyata, Variety ta ruwaito, wani daga cikin shirin ya gaya wa jaridar, "Dukkanin ɗakin studio sun yi shiru".
