Ya kasance a kan hanya.
Mu ma haka muke", in ji shi.
Kafin wasan kwaikwayon, rapper ya sanar a shafin Twitter cewa ya canza sunansa, yana mai cewa yanzu "wanda aka sani da Kanye West".
