HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton ƙaruwar sabbin mutane da kashi 14 cikin ɗari
Kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa yawan mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya ƙaru da kashi 14 cikin ɗari.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 ne ke fama da cutar a kasar, in ji jami'an lafiya.
An samu rahoton sabbin mutane kusan 40 000 a cikin kwata na biyu na shekarar 2018 kadai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka sun samo asali ne daga yaduwar cutar ta hanyar jima'i, wanda hakan ya nuna canji daga abin da ya faru a dā.
A al'ada, cutar HIV tana yaɗuwa da sauri a wasu ɓangarorin ƙasar Sin ta wurin ƙarin jini da ke ɗauke da cutar.
Amma adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Duk da haka, a cikin yanayin canji na shekara-shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An haramta luwadi a China a 1997, amma an ce ana nuna wa LGBT wariya sosai.
Bincike ya nuna cewa domin ra'ayoyi masu kyau na ƙasar, kashi 70 zuwa 90 cikin ɗari na maza da suka yi jima'i da maza suna auren mata.
Yawancin cututtuka da ake yaɗawa suna zuwa ne daga rashin kāriya ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan dangantaka.
Tun shekara ta 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da maganin cutar HIV ga kowa a matsayin wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin magance matsalar.
Maxine Waters ta musanta bayanan da wani abokin aikinta ya fitar game da 'yan majalisar dattijai 'yan Republican, kuma ta kai hari kan "karya mai hatsari" da kuma "ka'idojin makirci"
'Yar majalisar dokokin Amurka Maxine Waters ta musanta zargin da ake yi a ranar Asabar cewa wani memba na tawagarta ya wallafa bayanan sirri na wasu 'yan majalisar dattijai uku a shafukan Wikipedia na 'yan majalisar.
'Yar Democrat ta Los Angeles ta ce, masu ra'ayin mazan jiya da kuma shafukan yanar gizo na "dama" ne ke gabatar da zarge-zargen.
"Ƙarya, ƙarya, da kuma ƙarin ƙazantacciyar ƙarya", in ji Waters a cikin wata sanarwa a shafin Twitter.
Bayanan da aka wallafa sun haɗa da adireshin gida da kuma lambobin waya na Sanatoci Lindsey Graham na South Carolina da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, duka biyu na Utah.
Wannan bayanin ya bayyana a intanet a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani mutum da ba a san shi ba ya wallafa shi a Capitol Hill a lokacin da ake sauraron wani kwamiti na majalisar dattawa game da zargin da ake yi wa Brett Kavanaugh na yin lalata da ya yi wa babban kotun koli.
An samu wannan bayanan ne bayan da 'yan majalisar su uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan yanar gizo masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar su Gateway Pundit da RedState sun ba da rahoton cewa adireshin IP ɗin da ke gano tushen abubuwan da aka buga yana da alaƙa da ofishin Waters kuma sun buga bayanan wani memba na ma'aikatan Waters, The Hill ta ruwaito.
"Wannan zargi marar tushe karya ne kuma karya ce", in ji Waters.
"Abokin aikina, wanda aka lalata sunansa, bayanansa da kuma tsaronsa ta hanyar wannan ƙiren ƙarya da yaudara, ba shi da alhakin wannan ɓarnatar da bayanai.
Wannan zargi da babu tushe gaba ɗaya ƙarya ne kuma karya ce".
Sanarwar Waters ta jawo hanzari kan layi, ciki har da na tsohon sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙaryatawar tana da fushi", in ji Fleischer.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba ta da halin zama 'yar majalisa.
Idan aka zargi mutum da wani abu da ba hakkinsa ba, ba za ka iya yin fushi ba.
Ba za ka iya yin tsayin daka ba.
Ba za ka iya tambayar mai tuhumar ba.
Dole ne ya nuna natsuwa da kwanciyar hankali".
Fleischer ya yi kama da yadda Waters ya amsa da sukar da 'yan Democrat suka yi wa mai shari'a Kavanaugh, wanda masu sukar suka zarge shi da yin kamar ya yi fushi sosai a lokacin sauraron shari'ar ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar Republican da zai maye gurbin Waters a zaben fidda gwani, shi ma ya bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafinsa na Twitter.
"Mai tsanani idan gaskiya ne", in ji tweet dinsa.
A cikin sanarwar da ya bayar, Waters ya ce ofishinsa ya sanar da "hukumomin da suka dace" game da waɗannan zarge-zargen.
"Mun tabbata cewa za a fallasa masu laifin", ya ci gaba, "kuma za a hukunta su bisa doka saboda dukan ayyukansu, waɗanda suke da haɗari da haɗari ga kowa da kowa da kuma kowane memba na ma'aikatan".
Johnny English ya sake yin fim din 'Rowann Atkinson'
Yanzu abu ne na yau da kullum a nemi ma'anar Brexit a kowane sabon fim da ke da ɗanɗano na Burtaniya, kuma hakan na iya kasancewa ga sabon fim ɗin fim ɗin Johnny English, wanda aka fara a 2003 da "Johnny English" kuma aka sake dawo da shi a 2011 da "The Return of Johnny English".
Shin irin wannan abin dariya na son kai game da mu mu zama marasa kyau ne sabon damar fitarwa ga al'ummar?
A kowane hali, Johnny English, wanda bai dace ba, tare da idanunsa masu banƙyama da kuma bayyanar da ya wuce kima ya sami izininsa don ƙirƙirar rikice-rikice, wanda aka sabunta a karo na biyu - tare da sunansa yana nuna, fiye da komai, cewa wannan babban zane ne na ban dariya wanda aka tsara don masu son fim waɗanda ba Ingilishi ba.
Shi ne, hakika, ɗan leƙen asiri wanda, duk da son zuciyarsa na son yin ado, yana da ɗan Cloiseau, ɗan ɗan Mr. Bean, da kuma ɗan ɗan ɗan littafin da ya ba da labari guda ɗaya ga jigon fim ɗin "Moments of Glory" a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta London ta 2012.
Bugu da ƙari, halayensa ya samo asali ne daga matafiyi da kuma mutum mai ban mamaki na duniya wanda Atkinson ya taka a cikin tallan TV don Barclaycard, wanda ya bar rikici a cikin hanyarsa.
Akwai abubuwa masu ban sha'awa guda ɗaya ko biyu a cikin wannan sabon fitowar JE.
Na fi son wurin da Johnny English yake zuwa wurin wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu da ya saka makamai na dā, da kuma yadda ƙwanƙolin rotor ɗin suke yi wa ƙwanƙolin ƙwanƙwasa ƙwanƙwasa.
Kyautar Atkinson ga wasan kwaikwayo ta bayyana, amma abin dariya yana da rauni kuma ba shi da mahimmanci, musamman idan aka yi la'akari da cewa shirye-shiryen fim "mai tsanani" kamar 007 da Mission Impossible yanzu suna ba da tabbaci ga wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin kayan aiki.
Mun yi tunanin cewa ana nuna wa yara dariya ba manya ba, kuma a ganina, abubuwan ban mamaki na Johnny English ba su da ƙwarewa da kuma mayar da hankali kamar lambobin fim ɗin Atkinson a cikin hali na Bean.
Yanzu, abin da ake tsammani, wanda ke ci gaba da kasancewa, shi ne cewa Birtaniya tana cikin matsala mai tsanani.
Wani dan fashin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin sashen leken asiri na Birtaniya, ya bayyana sunayen duk jami'an Birtaniya da ke wurin, abin da ya ba wa jami'in aikin mamaki, wani aiki ne da Kevin Eldon bai cika ba.
Wannan shi ne na karshe ga firaminista mai nuna girman kai da rikici, wanda ya riga ya sha wahala daga rashin amincewa da siyasa: Emma Thompson ta yi iya ƙoƙarinta a wannan rawar da ta yi kama da Theresa May, amma ba ta ba da labari mai yawa don manyan jirage.
Masu ba da shawara a cikin ayyukan sirrinku sun sanar da ku cewa tun da yake an yi wa kowane ɗan fashin aiki laifi, za ku bukaci ku cire wani daga cikin 'yancin.
Kuma wannan mutumin Johnny English ne, wanda yake aiki a matsayin malamin makaranta a makarantar da ta fi kyau, amma yana koyar da darussa na yau da kullum game da yadda za a zama ɗan leƙen asiri.
An kai English cikin sauri zuwa Whitehall don samun umarnin gaggawa kuma ya sake haɗuwa da mataimakinsa Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake takawa.
Bough yanzu ya yi aure, yana da dangantaka da wani kwamandan jirgin ruwa, wani abu mai ban sha'awa wanda Vicki Pepperdine ya yi watsi da shi.
Saboda haka, Batman da Robin na bala'i a cikin Sirrin Sirrin Mai Martaba sun sake komawa aiki, suna fuskantar kyakkyawar mace mai ban tsoro Ophelia Bulletova, rawar da Olga Kurylenko ta taka.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista yana cikin haɗari da yaudarar wani mai karfin fasaha mai biliyan biliyan wanda ke da'awar cewa zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Birtaniya: Jason Volta mai ban tsoro, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
English da Bough sun fara tafiya ta rashin hankali: suna ɓoye a matsayin masu cin abinci, suna ƙone gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai ban sha'awa, suna haifar da rikicewa ta hanyar shiga cikin jirgin ruwan Volta mai tsada, kuma English ya haifar da rashin tsari na gaskiya lokacin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da tabarau na gaskiya don sanin abin da ke cikin gidan Volta.
An tsara dukan wuraren da za a tsaya domin wannan wasan kwaikwayon, amma duk da cewa yana da kyau kuma yana da ban sha'awa, akwai isashen TV na yara a wurin.
Sakamakon ya yi daidai.
Kamar sauran fina-finan Johnny English, na yi mamakin ko za a iya ba da rawar da Rowan Atkinson a cikin fim ɗin Birtaniya don ta yi daidai da baiwar da take da ita.
Ma'aikata sun musanta cewa suna samar da shirin cewa 'yan Birtaniya za su yi aiki kwana hudu a mako, amma su samu kwana biyar
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn na iya yin la'akari da wani shiri na musamman na bai wa 'yan Birtaniya aiki na kwana hudu a mako, amma tare da biyan kwanaki biyar.
Rahotanni sun nuna cewa jam'iyyar tana son masu aiki su ba da ceton da suka samu daga juyin juya halin fasaha na wucin gadi (AI) ga ma'aikata ta hanyar ba su karin ranar hutu.
Ma'aikata za su samu hutun mako na kwana uku, amma a biya su.
Majiyoyi sun ce wannan ra'ayin zai "dace" da shirin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar, wanda ke mayar da kasar ga ma'aikata.
Canji zuwa mako guda na aiki na kwana hudu ya sami amincewa daga taron ma'aikata a matsayin hanyar da ma'aikata za su yi amfani da canjin tattalin arziki.
Wani babban jami'in jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa The Sunday Times cewa: "Muna fatan sanar da sake duba manufofin kafin karshen shekara.
"Ba zai faru ba da dare ba, amma aikin kwana huɗu na mako-mako abu ne da ya dace da tsarin jam'iyyar na daidaita tattalin arziki don amfanin ma'aikata, da kuma dabarun jam'iyyar na masana'antu".
Jam'iyyar Labor ba za ta kasance farkon wanda ya goyi bayan irin wannan ra'ayin ba, tun da Jam'iyyar Green Party ta riga ta ba da shawarar mako hudu na aiki a lokacin kamfen dinta na zaben majalisar dokoki na 2017.
Amma, wannan burin ba shi da goyon baya a jam'iyyar Labour baki ɗaya a yanzu.
Wani mai magana da yawun jam'iyyar ya ce: "Aikin kwana huɗu ba shi da wani ɓangare na manufofin jam'iyyar kuma ba ma yin la'akari da shi".
Ministan kudi na inuwa John McDonnell ya yi amfani da taron jam'iyyarsa na makon da ya gabata don bayyana ra'ayinsa na juyin juya halin tattalin arziki na zamantakewa.
McDonnell ya ce yana da niyyar dawo da iko daga hannun "masu kula da ba su da fuska" da kuma "masu fashin baki" na kamfanonin samar da kayayyaki.
Shirye-shiryensa sun hada da rashin dawo da dukkan hannun jarin masu hannun jari na kamfanonin ruwa, saboda jam'iyyar Labour za ta iya yin "yanke-yanke" bisa ga tunanin aikata laifuka.
McDonnell ya kuma tabbatar da tsare-tsaren sanya ma'aikata a kan kwamitocin kamfanoni da kuma kafa asusun mallakar Inclusive wanda zai canja kashi 10 cikin 100 na hannun jari na kamfanoni masu zaman kansu zuwa ma'aikata, wanda zai iya samun ribar shekara-shekara har zuwa £500.
Lindsey Graham da John Kennedy sun gaya wa shirin "60 Minutes" ko binciken da FBI ta yi game da Kavanaugh zai iya canja musu ra'ayinsu
Binciken da FBI ke yi kan zargin da ake yi wa mai shari'a Brett Kavanaugh ya jinkirta kada kuri'ar zabensa na neman kujerar kotun koli na kasar nan da akalla mako guda, lamarin da ya jawo tambayoyi kan ko sakamakon zai iya sa 'yan majalisar dattijai na Republican su janye goyon bayansu.
A wata hira da aka bayar a ranar Lahadi, wakilin shirin "60 Minutes" Scott Pelley ya tambayi 'yan majalisar wakilai John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham ko hukumar ta FBI za ta iya gano wani abu da zai sa su canja ra'ayinsu.
Kennedy ya fi abokinsa na South Carolina faɗin gaskiya.
"Ina nufin, ba shakka", in ji Kennedy.
"Na ce a kan hanyar zuwa kotu, na ce, na yi magana da Alkalin Kavanaugh.
Na kira shi bayan wannan ya faru, lokacin da wannan zargi ya bayyana, kuma na tambaye shi, "ka yi hakan?"
Ya kasance mai tsai da shawara, mai ƙuduri, mai gaskiya".
Amma dai, ƙuri'ar Graham kamar ba za ta iya canjawa ba.
"Na yanke shawara game da Brett Kavanaugh kuma za a bukaci tuhuma mai ban tsoro", in ji shi.
"Dr. Ford, ban san abin da ya faru ba, amma na san abu ɗaya: Brett ya yi ƙin yarda da gaskiya", in ji Graham, yana nufin Christine Blasey Ford.
"Kuma duk wanda ta ambata ba ta iya tabbatar da hakan ba.
Shekaru 36 ke nan.
Ba na ganin wani sabon abu da ya canja".
