Sauran fitattun sunayen Jam'iyyar Democrat da ake muhawara a kansu dangane da yiwuwar takara a 2020 sun hada da tsohon Mataimakin Shugaban kasa Joe Biden da Sanata na Vermont Bernie Sanders.
Biden ya ce zai yanke shawara a cikin watan Janairu, in ji kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press.
Sarah Palin ta yi magana game da damuwa na Track Palin a taron Donald Trump
Track Palin, mai shekara 26, ya shafe shekara guda a Iraki bayan da aka tura shi aiki a watan Satumba.
A ranar Litinin da daddare, an kama shi kuma an tuhume shi da laifin wani abin da ya faru na tashin hankali na cikin gida.
"Abin da ɗana yake fuskanta, abin da yake fuskanta bayan ya dawo, zan iya ji da sauran iyalai da ke fama da sakamakon tashin hankali da kuma wasu raunuka da sojojinmu ke dawowa da su", in ji ta a wani taron goyon bayan Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin ta kira wannan kame-kame "giwa a cikin dakin" kuma ta ce ɗanta da sauran tsoffin sojoji "suna dawowa da bambanci, suna dawowa da tsananin ƙarfi, suna sake tambayar kansu ko akwai wannan girmamawa ga abin da takwarorinsu sojoji da masu tashi da jirgin sama, da duk sauran membobin sojoji, suka ba wa ƙasar".
An kama Track Palin a ranar Litinin a Wasilla, Alaska, kuma an tuhume shi da cin zarafin wata mata a gida da kuma mallakar bindiga yayin da yake shan giya, a cewar Dan Bennett, mai magana da yawun sashen 'yan sanda na Wasilla.
Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan ƙalubalantar sabon tsarin neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da kuma Gundumar Columbia suna goyon bayan takaddama kan sabuwar manufar Amurka ta hana bautar da wadanda ke tserewa daga cin zarafin 'yan bindiga ko na cikin gida.
Wakilan jihohi 18 da na gundumar sun aika da sanarwa ta amicus curiae (abokan kotu) a ranar Juma'a a Washington, D.C., a goyon bayan wani mai neman mafaka da ke kalubalantar wannan manufa, NBC News ta ruwaito.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara a shari'ar Grace da Sessions da Kungiyar 'Yancin Jama'ar Amurka ta shigar a watan Agusta ba.
Mutumin ya ce abokin tarayyarsa "da 'ya'yansa, 'yan wata ƙungiya mai ta'addanci", sun yi masa fyade, amma hukumomin Amurka sun ƙi amincewa da neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga Yuli.
An kama mai ƙarar a Texas.
Masu goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, da ke samar da mafaka mai yawa a Amurka, a matsayin ƙasashe da ke fuskantar matsalolin gangs da tashin hankali na cikin gida.
Sabuwar manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta soke shawarar da Hukumar Kula da Kula da Shige da Fice ta Amurka ta yanke a shekarar 2014 da ta bai wa baƙi marasa tushe da suka tsere daga tashin hankali na cikin gida damar neman mafaka.
Babban lauyan gundumar Columbia Karl Racine ya ce a wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar "ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na kasa da kasa".
"Dokar tarayya ta bukaci a yi la'akari da duk wani neman mafaka bisa ga takamaiman gaskiya da kuma yanayin da ke ƙarƙashinsa; wannan haramcin ya sabawa wannan ka'ida", in ji amicus curiae.
Lauyoyin sun kuma yi jayayya a cikin wannan sanarwa cewa hana 'yan sanda shiga baƙi yana shafar tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna mai da hankali kan cewa baƙi sun fi zama' yan kasuwa kuma "suna samar da aikin da ake buƙata".
Babban lauya Jeff Sessions ya umarci alƙalan shige da fice su daina ba wa wadanda ake zalunta da kuma 'yan bindiga mafaka a watan Yuni.
"Ana samun mafaka ga waɗanda suka bar ƙasarsu saboda tsanantawa ko fargabar tsanantawa bisa ga kabilanci, addini, ƙasa, ko kuma kasancewa cikin wani takamaiman rukuni na zamantakewa ko kuma ra'ayi na siyasa", in ji Sessions a sanarwar manufarsa ta 11 ga Yuni.
Ba a taɓa nufin mafaka ta magance dukan matsaloli ba, ko ma dukan matsaloli masu tsanani da mutane suke fuskanta a kowace rana a dukan duniya.
