Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da "ta'addanci" da "tallace-tallacen farfaganda"
Makon daya bayan wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani sanarwa mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka mai dauke da labaran kasuwanci da ke inganta amfanin kasuwanci tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da kafofin yada labarai na Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba game da biyan kudin da ake biyan jaridar China Daily a Des Moines Register, jaridar da ta fi yawa a jihar Iowa, bayan ya zargi China da neman tsoma baki a zaben da za a yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
Zargin da Trump ya yi cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka ya nuna farkon abin da jami'an Amurka a cikin kalaman da suka yi wa Reuters, ya nuna sabon mataki a cikin fadada yakin da Washington ke yi na matsa lamba kan China.
Ko da yake al'ada ce gwamnatocin kasashen waje su yi tallace-tallace don inganta kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a yanzu suna cikin yakin cinikayya mai tsanani wanda ya ga bangarorin biyu suna sanya haraji kan kayayyakin da ake shigowa da su.
An tsara takunkumin da China ta saka a farkon yakin cinikayya don ta shafi masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohin da ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana na China da na Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
China, in ji Branstad a cikin wani labari a cikin Des Moines Register na ranar Lahadi, "yanzu tana sa kafa a kan wannan matsin lamba ta hanyar buga tallace-tallace a cikin jaridarmu mai 'yanci".
"Ta hanyar yada wannan farfagandar, gwamnatin kasar Sin tana amfani da ƙaunatacciyar al'adar Amurka na 'yancin magana da latsa ta hanyar buga wani talla da aka biya a cikin Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A gefe guda, a wurin zama a nan Beijing, mun sami 'yan muryoyin 'yan adawa kaɗan, kuma ba za mu taɓa ganin ainihin nuna bambancin ra'ayin da Sinawa za su iya yi game da yanayin tattalin arzikin ƙasarsu ba, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin ikon jam'iyyar Kwaminis ta Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kuma kara da cewa "wani babban jaridar kasar Sin ya ki amincewa da buga" labarin nasa, ko da yake bai bayyana ko wace ce ba.
'Yan Republican sun yi watsi da masu jefa kuri'a mata kafin zaben fidda gwani na Kavanaugh, manazarta sun gargadi
A daidai lokacin da manyan 'yan Republican ke goyon bayan da kuma kare wanda aka nada a kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh a kan zargin cin zarafin mata da dama, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa hakan na iya haifar da mummunan martani, musamman daga mata, a lokacin zaben da ke tafe.
An yi ta ta jinjinawa game da batun kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun bayyana a fili cewa suna son su ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
Waɗannan abubuwa ba su da hanyar komawa baya", in ji Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell a Jami'ar Syracuse, ga wata kasida da aka buga a ranar Asabar.
Reeher ya ce yana shakkar cewa matsin lamba na karshe da Sanata Jeff Flake (Republican na Arizona) ya yi na gudanar da bincike na FBI zai isa ya kwantar da hankalin masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba - ba za su manta ba gobe ko a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara kuma mai magana da yawun ƙungiyar ci gaba ta MoveOn, a ranar Juma'a, kamar yadda jaridar Washington, D.C. ta ruwaito.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, masu zanga-zanga sun yi waka "November is at the door!" yayin da suke zanga-zanga a harabar majalisar dattawa, yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka zaɓi ci gaba da nadin Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, Mic ta ruwaito.
"Himma da himmar 'yan Democrat za su yi nasara", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wani manazarcin siyasa da ba shi da wata ƙungiya.
"Mutane suna cewa ta riga ta yi tsayi; gaskiya ne.
Amma za ta iya zama mafi girma, musamman tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a a yankunan karkara da kuma matasa masu jefa kuri'a, masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29, waɗanda ko da yake ba sa son shugaban ƙasa, sau da yawa ba sa jefa kuri'a".
Tun kafin Ford ya ba da shaida a fili game da zargin da ya yi wa wanda ya zaɓa a Kotun Koli, manazarta sun ce za a iya samun mummunar amsa idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da tabbatar da shi.
"Wannan ya zama matsala ga jam'iyyar Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National a farkon makon da ya gabata, a cewar NBC News.
"Ba wai kawai game da kuri'ar kwamitin ba ne, ko kuma ko Kavanaugh zai dauki matsayinsa na alkalin kotu, amma kuma game da yadda 'yan Republican suka yi da batun da kuma yadda suka bi da shi", in ji Guy Cecil, daraktan Priorities USA, wani rukuni da ke taimakawa wajen zaben 'yan Democrat, ga tashar labarai.
Amma, jama'ar Amirka sun rarrabu a kan wanda za su yarda da shi bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, tare da wani karamin rinjaye da ke goyon bayan na farko.
Wani sabon bincike na YouGov ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun gaskata da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun gaskata da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin dari sun ce suna ganin Kavanaugh ya yi ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a shaidar da ya bayar, yayin da kashi 30 cikin dari suka ce haka ne game da Ford.
Bayan da Flake ya gabatar da shawarar, FBI ta fara binciken zargin da Ford ya yi, da kuma wani mai zargin, Deborah Ramirez, in ji jaridar Guardian.
Ford ya shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa a makon da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade yayin da take cikin maye, lokacin da take 'yar shekara 17.
Ramirez ya yi ikirarin cewa wanda aka naɗa a matsayin babban alkalin kotun ya fallasa al'aurarsa lokacin da su biyun suka halarci wani biki a lokacin da su biyun suke karatu a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo na duniya yana son ƙirƙirar sabuwar intanet don gasa da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kafa wani kamfanin farawa da zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin wannan fitaccen masanin fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ke amfani da hanyar Berners-Lee mai budewa, Solid.
Wannan yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda ake adana bayanan su da kuma wanda ke da damar zuwa wane bayani.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi da'awar cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi game da farawar.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don ba mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu "ma'ajiyar bayanan kan layi", ko POD.
Wannan zai iya ƙunsar jerin lambobin sadarwa, jerin ayyuka, kalanda, laburaren waƙa, da wasu kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify suna nan a cikin burauzar yanar gizo ɗaya, a lokaci guda.
Abin ban mamaki game da ajiyar bayanan sirri na kan layi shi ne, mai amfani ne kaɗai zai iya yanke shawara game da wanda zai iya samun irin bayanin da yake so.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "koyon abubuwa da kanka ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, ita ce samar da kayan aiki, aiyuka da kuma basira da suka dace don taimakawa wajen samar da Solid ga kowa.
Kamfanin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro wanda IBM ta saya, wasu masu shirye-shiryen cikin gida da aka yi wa haya don yin aiki a kan aikin, da kuma al'ummar masu shirye-shiryen aikin sa kai.
Farawa daga wannan makon, masu fasahar zamani a duk faɗin duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya bayyana cewa shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da "Facebook da Google game da ko za su gabatar da sauyi na gaba daya inda duk tsarin kasuwancin su ya juya baya daga dare.
"Ba ma neman izinin su".
A wani rubutu a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "umurnin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu da zai taimaka wajen kare mutunci da ingancin sabon yanar gizo da aka kirkira tare da Solid".
A 1994, Berners-Lee ya canja Intanet sa'ad da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na Intanet.
Ko da lokacin da ya kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa wanda ya kafa kuma darektan World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Bude.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da wannan zamani na yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: girmamawa ga limamin da aka ba da lambar Victoria Cross a yakin duniya na farko
Limamin Cocin Ingila guda daya da ya sami Victoria Cross a lokacin yakin duniya na farko a matsayin mai yaki an karrama shi a garinsu bayan shekaru 100.
Lt. Col. Reverend Bernard Vann ya sami lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 tare da harin Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Amma, wani dan bindiga ya kashe shi bayan kwana huɗu, kuma ban taɓa sanin cewa ya sami babban gata na soja na Birtaniya ba.
Yaransa biyu sun cire wani allon tunawa a wani wurin shakatawa a Rushden, Northamptonshire, ranar Asabar.
Ɗaya daga cikinsu, Michael Vann, ya ce "alamar alama ce" cewa an gabatar da allon daidai shekara 100 bayan nasarar da ta ba kakansa lambar yabo.
A ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, in ji jaridar London Gazette, Laftanar Janar Vann ya ja-goranci rundunarsa a kan Canal Saint-Quentin "cikin hazo mai-zafi, a ƙarƙashin wuta mai-ƙarfi daga makamai masu-kauri da kuma na'urori masu-makamai".
Sai ya ruga zuwa layin wuta, kuma "da ƙarfin zuciya", ya jagoranci layin gaba kafin ya kai hari kan bindiga shi kaɗai kuma ya kashe sojoji uku na rukunin.
An kashe Laftanar Kanar Vann da wani dan bindiga na Jamus a ranar 4 ga watan Oktoba, 1918, fiye da wata daya kafin karshen yakin.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce abin da kakansa ya yi "wani abu ne da na sani ba zan taɓa iya daidaitawa ba, amma kuma darasi ne na tawali'u".
Shi da ɗan'uwansa, Dr. James Vann, sun ajiye rawanin furanni bayan taron, wanda ƙungiyar matasa ta Brentwood Imperial ta jagoranci.
Michael Vann ya ce "ya ji daɗi sosai da ya halarci bikin" kuma ya kara da cewa "za a nuna ƙarfin hali na jarumi na gaske ta hanyar goyon bayan da mutane da yawa za su bayar".
Masu sha'awar wasan Mixed Martial Arts da suka zauna duk dare suna kallon Bellator 206 suna kallon Porca Peppa
Ka yi tunanin wannan: Ka yi barci dukan dare don ka kalli Bellator 206, wanda ke cike da taurari, kuma a ƙarshe, an hana ka kallon babban taron.
