"Ina ganin idan muka yi tunani a kan maimaitawa, zan iya magance matsalar", in ji Coker.
"Amma, sa'a ta shida ce da safe a ranar Lahadi a can, kuma ba za mu iya warware matsalar ba har sai lokacinmu na Lahadi, wanda Litinin ne a lokacin Birtaniya.
Amma muna aiki a kan hakan.
Ba ƙarya nake yi ba sa'ad da na ce lokacin da aka canja tsarin, an yi ta yin saƙo da yawa, amma babu wanda ya yi magana mai kyau.
Muna ƙoƙarin magance matsalar, mun yi tunanin cewa kuskure ne na fasaha.
Amma ba haka ba ne. Matsalar gwamnati ce.
Na yi alkawari ba zai faru ba.
Za mu rage yawan wasannin zuwa biyar maimakon shida kamar yadda muke yi a kullum, kuma mun yi ƙoƙari mu wuce tsammanin magoya bayanmu kuma mun wuce gona da iri.
Wannan abin baƙin ciki ne".
Desert Island Discs: Tom Daley ya ji "ƙasa" game da jima'i
Dan wasan ruwa na Olympics Tom Daley ya ce ya girma yana jin kasa da kowa saboda jima'i, amma hakan ya ba shi kwarin gwiwa don ya zama mai nasara.
Dan wasan mai shekara 24 ya ce bai fahimci ba har ya shiga makarantar sakandare cewa "ba kowa ba ne kamar ni".
A cikin hira da farko da aka yi da Desert Island Discs na Radio 4 wanda Lauren Laverne ta gabatar, ta ce ta yi magana ne a kan 'yancin 'yan luwadi don ba da "bege" ga wasu.
Ya kuma ce zama uba ya sa ya daina damuwa game da cin gasar Olympics.
Mai gabatar da shirin Kirsty Young ta dauki hutun watanni da dama saboda rashin lafiya.
Da yake fitowa a matsayin ɗan iska a cikin shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya ba da rahoton cewa ya ji "ƙasa" ga kowa saboda "ba a yarda da shi ba don son samari da 'yan mata.
A cikin kalmominsa, "har wa yau, wannan ra'ayin na kasa da bambanci shi ne ainihin abin da ya ba ni iko da ƙarfi na cimma nasara".
Manufarsa ita ce ta tabbatar da cewa shi "wani ne", in ji shi, don kada ya sa kowa ya yi sanyin gwiwa idan suka gano jima'i a baya ko kuma a baya.
Gwarzon dan wasan tagulla na Olympics ya zama fitaccen mai fafutukar LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da halartarsa a wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Australia don yin kira ga kasashe da yawa da su dakatar da luwadi.
Ya ce ya yi hakan ne domin yana farin ciki da ya yi rayuwa a fili ba tare da sakamako ba kuma yana son ya ba da "bege" ga wasu.
Gwarzon mai cin kofin duniya sau uku ya ce, "ya kama ni da mamaki" lokacin da na fara soyayya da wani mutum, mai shirya fim din Amurka Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekarar 2013.
Daley ta auri wanda ya lashe Oscar a shekarar da ta gabata, wanda ya girme ta da shekara 20, duk da cewa ta ce bambancin shekarun bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Idan muka fuskanci irin wannan lokacin da muke matasa" - ya fara shiga wasannin Olympics yana ɗan shekara 14, kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka - ya ce, yana da wuya a sami wani ɗan shekara ɗaya da ya fuskanci irin wannan tashin hankali.
Ma'auratan sun haifi ɗa a watan Yuni na shekarar da ta gabata, wanda ake kira Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma Daley ya ce "dukkanin ra'ayinsa" ya canja.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, abin da ya fi muhimmanci shi ne samun lambar zinare", in ji shi.
"Amma, ka sani, akwai abubuwa da suka fi zinare na Olympics muhimmanci.
"Robin ne lambar zinare ta na gasar Olympics".
Sunan ɗansa ya yi kama da na mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekara 40 bayan an gano shi da ciwon daji na kwakwalwa.
Daley ya bayyana cewa mahaifinsa bai yarda da cewa zai mutu ba, kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan da ya tambaya shi ne ko sun riga sun samu tikitin zuwa gasar London ta 2012 domin yana son ya kasance a gaba.
"Ba zan iya gaya masa cewa ba za ka kasance a nan ba don ka kasance a kan layin farko, Baba", in ji shi.
"Na riƙe hannunsa ne sa'ad da ya daina numfashi, kuma sai da ya daina numfashi kuma ya mutu ne na fahimci cewa ba shi da iko", in ji shi.
A shekara mai zuwa, Daley ya yi gasa a wasannin Olympics na 2012 kuma ya sami lambar tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan shi ne abin da na yi mafarki a rayuwata: yin iyo a gaban taron 'yan'uwana a wasannin Olympics...babu abin da ya fi wannan", in ji shi.
Duk wannan kuma ya kasance wahayi ne ga waƙar da ta fara zaɓa - Proud ta Heather Small - wanda ta yi hulɗa da shi yayin shirye-shiryen wasannin Olympics, kuma har yanzu yana ba ta fata.
An gabatar da shirin Desert Island Discs a BBC Radio 4 a ranar Lahadi da karfe 11:15 na yammacin yammacin yammacin Birtaniya.
Mickelson a kan benci a gasar Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai buga wani babban tarihi a ranar Asabar lokacin da ya buga wasansa na 47 a gasar Ryder Cup, amma zai bukaci ya dawo cikin siffarsa don hana alamar nuna rashin sa'a.
Mickelson, wanda ya buga wasan ne a karo na 12, wanda ya kafa tarihi, ya yi kasa a raga a ranar Asabar, a wasan kwallon kafa da na hudu da kuma na hudu da Kyaftin Jim Furyk ya yi.
Maimakon ya kasance a tsakiyar wasan kamar yadda ya saba a wasannin Amurka, wanda ya lashe gasar zakarun maza sau biyar ya raba ranar tsakanin goyon baya da kuma aiki a wasan da yake yi a filin wasa, yana fatan ya gyara abin da ke damunsa.
Ba a taɓa yin wasan tsalle-tsalle ba a lokacin da yake kan gaba a wasan, amma ɗan shekara 48 bai dace da filin Le Golf National ba, inda dogon tsalle-tsalle ke azabtar da masu cin zarafin.
Kuma idan filin wasa ba shi da ban tsoro, Mickelson a wasa na tara na ranar Lahadi zai fafata da dan wasan British Open Francesco Molinari, wanda ya hada da dan wasan farko Tommy Fleetwood, inda suka lashe wasanni hudu da suka buga a makon nan.
Idan 'yan Amurkan, da suka yi nisa da maki hudu a fara wasannin su na 12 na wasan guda, suka fara wasa mai kyau, wasan Mickelson zai iya zama muhimmiyar wasa.
Furyk ya nuna tabbaci a kan mutuminsa, amma ba zai iya cewa ya fi haka ba.
Furyk ya ce: "Ya fahimci aikin da nake da shi a yau, ya yi mini taushi a baya, ya ɗora min hannu, kuma ya ce zai kasance a shirye gobe.
"Ya amince da kansa sosai.
Shi ne babban dan wasa da ya ba da gudummawa ga waɗannan kungiyoyi a baya, da kuma wannan makon.
Wataƙila ban taɓa ganin shi ya buga wasanni biyu ba.
Na yi tunani sosai, amma haka ya faru kuma haka muka ga ya kamata mu ci gaba.
Yana son ya kasance a cikin wasan, kamar kowa".
Mickelson zai doke Nick Faldo a ranar Lahadi da ya fi kowacce wasa a gasar Ryder Cup.
Wannan zai iya kawo ƙarshen wasan Ryder Cup wanda bai taɓa yin nasara ba kamar yadda ya yi a wasan kansa.
Mickelson ya samu nasara 18 da rashin nasara 20 da kuma cin kwallaye bakwai, duk da cewa Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa ya samar da wasu fa'idodi marasa ma'ana ga tawagar.
"Yana da ba'a, mai ban dariya da kuma farin ciki, yana son yin wasa da mutane kuma yana da kyakkyawan mutum don samun a cikin dakin tawagar", in ji shi.
"Ina tsammanin 'yan wasan sun ji daɗin yin wasa da shi a wannan makon, wanda abin farin ciki ne a gani.
Yana ba da fiye da wasa kawai".
