Ma'aikatar Shari'a ta bukaci a yanke wa wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci hukuncin kisa a birnin New York.
Ma'aikatar Shari'a ta birnin New York ta nemi a yanke wa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci da ya kashe mutane takwas a birnin - hukuncin da ba a yi ba a jihar tun shekarar 1953 don aikata laifi na tarayya.
An zargi Saipov, mai shekara 30, da amfani da babbar motar haya da aka yi haya daga Home Depot don kai hari a watan Oktoba a kan hanyar keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya yi wa masu tafiya da keke da kuma masu hawa.
Don a yanke masa hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe wadanda aka kashe da gangan kuma ya yi wa wasu da suka ji rauni da suka kai ga mutuwa, a cewar sanarwar da ke neman hukuncin kisa da aka sanya a yankin kudancin birnin New York.
Za a iya yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan waɗannan laifuffuka biyu, in ji takardar shari'a.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun tarayya ta gurfanar da Saipov kan laifuka 22, ciki har da laifuka takwas na kisan kai a hidimar masu aikata laifuka, wanda ake amfani da shi a cikin shari'o'in masu aikata laifuka, da kuma laifuka guda daya na tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da kuma tunani sosai", in ji masu gabatar da kara, suna kwatanta yadda Saipov ya kashe shi a matsayin "mai banƙyama, mai zalunci da lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco rauni, lalacewa da kuma asarar abokai", in ji sanarwar.
Biyar cikin waɗanda aka kashe 'yan yawon buɗe ido ne daga ƙasar Ajantina.
Shekara goma kenan da yankin Kudu na New York ba su nemi hukuncin kisa ba a kan wani laifi.
An yanke wa Khalid Barnes hukuncin kisa kan masu safarar miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma an sauya hukuncinsa zuwa rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka kashe Julius da Ethel Rosenberg a New York City, bayan da aka yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan laifin yin leken asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet, shekaru biyu da suka gabata, a lokacin Yakin Cacar Farin.
An kashe Rosenbergs a kan kujera mai walƙiya a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar takardun kotu, Saipov, ɗan Uzbekistan, bai nuna baƙin ciki ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa ya ji wahayi zuwa kai harin ne bayan ya ga bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, a cewar mai gabatar da kara.
Ya kuma nemi izini don rataye tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin, 'yan sanda sun ruwaito.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan dukan tuhume-tuhume 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin kare Saipov, ya ce sun "yi matukar takaici" da hukuncin da mai gabatar da kara ya yanke.
"Muna ganin cewa yanke shawarar neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar hukuncin daurin rai da rai ba tare da damar samun 'yanci ba zai kara tsawaita raunin da ke tattare da wadannan abubuwan da suka faru ga duk wanda ke da hannu", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov ta riga ta nemi masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
Dan majalisa mai ra'ayin mazan jiya ya ce ya kamata NIGEL FARAGE ya jagoranci tattaunawar Brexit
Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin "karfafa rundunar jama'a" a yau a lokacin zanga-zanga a taron majalisa na Conservatives.
Tsohon shugaban UKIP ya ce ya kamata 'yan siyasa su "ji matsin lamba" daga masu shakkar Turai, yayin da daya daga cikin 'yan majalisar Theresa May ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata ya jagoranci tattaunawar da EU.
Dan majalisa mai ra'ayin mazan jiya Peter Bone ya ce a zanga-zangar Birmingham cewa Birtaniya "da ta riga ta fice" idan Farage ya kasance Ministan Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da Mrs May ta fuskanta wajen sulhunta 'yan uwanta masu addini masu rarrabuwa ya sha jinjina daga masu ra'ayin tsayawa, wadanda suka shirya wani gangamin nuna rashin amincewa da Brexit a birnin.
Firayim Minista ta yi ta ta fama da yadda za ta ci gaba da shirin ta na cin amanar kasashen waje, wanda aka fi sani da Plan Chequers, a yayin da ake kai wa hari daga masu goyon bayan Brexit, masu goyon bayan tsayawa da kuma EU.
Abokan hulda sun nace cewa za ta ci gaba da kokarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da zanga-zangar, ta tilasta wa masu kyamar Turai da jam'iyyar Labour su zabi tsakanin kunshin ta da "hargitsi".
Mista Bone ya ce a taron Leave Means Leave a Solihull cewa yana son "kawar da Shirin".
Bone ya ba da shawarar cewa ya kamata a ba Farage hakki a cikin tattaunawar da Brussels.
"Da a ce shi ne ke da alhakin, da mun riga mun bar wurin", in ji shi.
Dan majalisar Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Zan ci gaba da goyon bayan Brexit amma ya kamata mu kawo karshen Shirin".
Da yake kara tabbatar da adawarsa ga EU, ya ce: "Ba mu yi yaƙi a Yaƙe-yaƙe biyu na Duniya ba domin mu zama masu biyayya.
Muna son mu kafa dokokin ƙasarmu".
Bone ya musanta zargin cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun bayan zaben raba gardama na 2016: "Tunanin cewa mutanen Burtaniya sun canza ra'ayinsu kuma suna son su kasance gaba ɗaya ba daidai ba ne".
'Yar jam'iyyar Conservative Brexit Andrea Jenkyns ta halarci wannan zanga-zanga, inda ta shaida wa manema labarai cewa: "Ina cewa kawai: uwargidan firaminista, ka saurari jama'a.
Shirin Chequers ba shi da kyau a gaban jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su amince da shi ba, ba shi da kyau a cikin jam'iyyarmu da kuma masu fafutuka da ke gudanar da kamfen ɗinmu a kan titi da kuma waɗanda muke bin su da zaɓenmu.
Ka bar shirin Chequers ka fara sauraro".
A wata sako ga Mrs May, ya kara da cewa: "Sai Firayim Ministocin da suka san yadda za su cika alkawuransu ne kawai za su ci gaba da aikinsu".
Farage ya ce a wajen zanga-zangar dole ne 'yan siyasa su "ji matsin lamba" idan suka yi hanzarin cin amanar shawarar da aka yanke a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
"Wannan ya zama batun amincewa tsakaninmu - mutane - da kuma siyasa", in ji shi.
"Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit kuma muna nan a yau mu gaya musu cewa ba za su tsira da hakan ba".
Da yake magana ga taron masu farin ciki, ya kara da cewa: "Ina son ku matsawa 'yan siyasa da ke gab da cin amanar Brexit.
Muna son mu tattara sojojin jama'ar kasar nan da suka ba mu nasara a kan Brexit, kuma ba za su huta ba har sai mun zama Burtaniya mai 'yancin kai, mai alfahari da kuma mulkin kanta".
A halin yanzu, masu goyon bayan tsayawa sun yi tafiya a Birmingham kafin su shirya taron sa'o'i biyu a tsakiyar gari.
Jama'a masu fafutuka sun yi amfani da katunan da ke dauke da sakon "Masu ra'ayin mazan jiya da suka yi adawa da Brexit" bayan kaddamar da kungiyar a karshen mako.
Wakilin jam'iyyar Labour a majalisar Lords, Andrew Adonis, ya soki 'yan Conservatives kan matsalolin tsaro da suka fuskanta da wani takarar jam'iyyar a taron bude majalisa.
"Waɗannan mutane ne ke gaya mana cewa za su sami tsarin kwamfuta da dukkan fasahohi a shirye don 'Canada More', don iyakar da ba ta da matsala, don cinikin da ba shi da iyaka a Ireland", in ji shi.
Wannan abin ban dariya ne.
Babu wani Brexit mai kyau", ya kammala.
