Patrick Dwyer ya ci kwallaye biyu a raga a Dundee
Dundee Stars sun dawo daga rashin nasara a ranar Juma'a a wasan farko da suka buga da Belfast Giants, inda suka ci wasan na biyu 5-3 a ranar Asabar a Dundee.
