Jirgin sama ya fadi a Micronesia: Air Niugini ta sanar yanzu cewa akwai wani mutum da ya bace bayan jirgin ya fadi a tafkin
Kamfanin jirgin sama da ya yi hatsarin jirgin a wani tafki a yankin Micronesia, Pacific, ya sanar da cewa akwai wani mutum da ya bace bayan ya sanar da cewa an ceto dukkan fasinjoji 47 da ma'aikatan jirgin daga jirgin da ke nutsewa.
A wata sanarwa, kamfanin Air Niugini ya ce tun ranar Asabar da yamma ba zai iya tabbatar da inda wani matafiyi namiji yake ba.
Kamfanin na yankin ya ce suna aiki tare da asibitoci, masu bincike da hukumomin yankin wajen gano mutumin.
Kamfanin jirgin bai amsa ba da sauri ga buƙatun don bayyana ƙarin cikakkun bayanai game da fasinja, kamar shekaru ko ƙasa.
Jiragen ruwa na gida sun taimaka wajen ceton sauran fasinjoji da ma'aikatan jirgin bayan jirgin ya yi karo da ruwa yayin da yake kokarin sauka a filin jirgin saman tsibirin Chuuk.
Hukumomi sun ce a ranar Juma'a mutane bakwai ne aka kwantar a asibiti.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce fasinjoji shida sun kasance a asibiti a ranar Asabar, dukkansu suna da lafiya.
Har yanzu ba a san ainihin dalilin faɗuwar ba ko kuma ainihin yadda abubuwa suka faru.
Kamfanin jirgin sama da kuma rundunar sojin ruwa na Amurka sun ce jirgin bai kai inda ya kamata ba kuma ya fadi a tafkin.
Wasu shaidu sun ce jirgin ya yi watsi da hanyarsa.
Wani matafiyi Ba'amurke mai suna Bill Jaynes ya ce jirgin yana sauka sosai.
"Wannan shi ne abu mafi kyau da ya taɓa faruwa", in ji Jaynes.
Jaynes ya ce shi da wasu sun yi nasarar ratsawa da ruwa a wuyansu suka kai ga hanyar fita daga jirgin da ke nitsewa.
Ya ce ma'aikatan jirgin sun firgita kuma suka fara ihu, kuma ya ji rauni a kai.
