Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Ƙungiyar Turai ta doke Amurka kuma ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 da ƙimar ƙarshe ta 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a gefen Paris, Faransa.
Yanzu Amurka ta ci nasara shida a Turai tun lokacin da ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai a 1993.
Turai ta sake samun nasara bayan da tawagar kyaftin din Denmark Thomas Bjorn ta samu maki 14.5 da ake bukata domin doke Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya nuna yana da matukar wahala a kusan dukkanin gasar, ya jefa tee-up zuwa ruwa a rami na 16, par 3, ya ba da nasara ga Francesco Molinari.
Dan wasan golf na Italiya Molinari ya yi fice a duk zagayensa, ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasa 4 da suka samu 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth ya ci 5 da 4 a hannun dan wasan da ya fi kowacce a Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Dan wasan da ya fi kowacce a duniya Dustin Johnson ya sha kashi 2 da 1 ga Ian Poulter na Ingila a wasan da zai iya zama gasar Ryder Cup ta karshe da ya buga.
Wani tsohon dan wasan Ryder Cup takwas, dan kasar Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama dan wasa mafiya lashe gasar Turai a duk lokacin da ya ci kwallaye 25.5 a rayuwarsa.
"Ba na yawan kuka, amma na kasa kame kaina a yau.
Shekara ce mai wuya.
Ina godiya ga Thomas da ya zaɓe ni kuma ya gaskata da ni.
Ina farin ciki da muka ci kofin.
Dukkanin aiki ne na kungiya kuma ina farin cikin cewa na iya taimakawa", in ji Garcia mai juyayi bayan nasarar Turai.
Ka ba da jawabi ga ɗan ƙasarka Jon Rham wanda ya doke shahararren ɗan wasan golf na Amurka Tiger Woods da 2 da 1 a wasan daya a ranar Lahadi.
Rahm, mai shekara 23 ya ce: "Ba zan iya kwatanta yadda nake alfahari da na doke Tiger Woods ba. Na girma ina kallon sa yana wasa.
Woods ya rasa duka wasanni hudu a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da rikodin 13-21-3 a gasar Ryder Cup.
Ƙididdigar da ba a saba gani ba daga ɗaya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa na dukan lokaci tare da manyan taken 14 da aka samu kuma kawai Jack Nicklaus ya doke shi.
Sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau da suka yi babban aiki a gasar, sauran 'yan wasan Amurka sun yi ta kokawa don su kai gafarar.
Kyaftin din Amurka Jim Furyk ya yi magana bayan wasan da tawagarsa ta yi, "Ina alfahari da su. Sun yi gwagwarmaya.
A wannan safiya, mun samu damar tsoratar da Turai.
Mun yi yaƙi.
Na taya Thomas murna.
Babban kyaftin ne.
Dukan 'yan wasan su 12 sun yi kyau sosai.
Za mu sake tsara kanmu kuma zan yi aiki tare da PGA of America da kuma Hukumar Ryder Cup don ci gaba da wannan.
Ina son 'yan wasanmu 12 kuma ina alfahari da zama kyaftinansu.
Dole ne in cire hat daga kan sauran tawagar.
Sun fi kyau".
Sabuntawa game da Red Tide: Ƙididdiga sun ragu a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
A cewar sabon rahoto daga Hukumar Kula da Kifi da Dajin Florida, an samu raguwar yawan Red Tide a wasu yankunan Tampa Bay.
FWC ta sanar da cewa an gano yanayin rage yaduwar tabo a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier County, wanda ke nuna raguwar taro.
Red Tide Spot yana da nisan mil 120 a bakin teku, daga Pinellas County a arewa zuwa Lee County a kudu.
Ana iya samun tabo a nisan mil goma daga gabar tekun Hillsborough amma a wurare da yawa fiye da na makon da ya gabata.
An kuma ga Red Tide a gundumar Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, mun samu matsakaitan taro a bakin tekun Pinella County, low zuwa high a bakin tekun Hillsborough County, low zuwa high a Manatee County, low zuwa high a bakin tekun Sarasota County, low zuwa matsakaici a Charlotte County, low zuwa high a bakin tekun Lee County, da low a Collier County.
Ana ci gaba da samun rahotanni game da ciwon numfashi a Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da kuma Collier.
A makon da ya gabata, babu wani rahoton rashin jin daɗin numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida.
